Roger S. PAGE, as Executor of the ESTATE of Amy L. SMITH, Deceased, Petitioner, v. COMMISSIONER OF INTERNAL REVENUE, Respondent. No. 8389. Circuit Court of Appeals, Ninth Circuit. Dec. 7, 1936. Robert H. Jackson, Asst. Atty. Gen., for respondent.

Before GARRECHT and HANEY, Circuit Judges, and NETERER, District Judge.

PER CURIAM.

Upon motion of respondent, and by direction of the court, ordered petition to review dismissed for failure of petitioner to file record and docket cause; mandate forthwith.
